Entries.default: "Anyone bring a spool of fishing line?"
"And now there be glowing crystals and mushrooms. I'd rather it be full fucking dark meself."
"So it's right, right, left... no wait. Right, left, left, straight. Oh, Hel. I'm lost already."
"I could swear we've been this way before."
"Captain, have we... no, ignore me - I am mistaken."
"I believe this place is leading in circles... or worse."
"It be like a kith's mind in here. All switchbacks and false starts."
"I'll just say another prayer that we can find our way back out..."
